      "text": "The Diversity Visa (DV) 2027 entry registration period is not open at this time. We are aware of reports of fraudulent claims that DV-2027 entry is open and of individuals and services falsely claiming they can increase your chances of selection. This is not true.  DV-2027 registration dates and details about changes to this year’s process will be announced by the Department of State when available.",
